== Psi-Tech Stack ==
[[PsiSys]] is the operating-system-level abstraction that runs across the [[Psi-Tech]] roster. PsiSys responsibilities map to fielded devices:

* '''Operator session''': [[HelmKit]] firmware + [[Psi Recorder]] + [[Resonant Card]] auth.
* '''Operator state''': [[Psi Stabilizer]] + [[Psi Harmonizer]] (PsiSys schedules per-session).
* '''Pair-bond''': [[Psi Tether]] (PsiSys mediates ephemeral pairing).
* '''Inference''': [[Psi Anomaly Detector]] (PsiSys deploys signed model bundles).
* '''Site''': [[Coherence Beacon]] + [[Psi Anchor]] + [[Schumann Lattice]] (PsiSys manages site-node lifecycle).
* '''Federation''': [[Synastry Mesh]] + [[EIN Relay Node]] (PsiSys handles signed-result routing).

